{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_102","type":"command_execution","command":"/bin/bash -lc \"sed -n '1,220p' ISSUE_COMMENTS.md && sed -n '1,260p' PR_COMMENTS.md\"","aggregated_output":"Changes committed in PR #<NN>.\n\nSummary: GO:0018581 has been obsoleted and replaced by GO:0047074. GO:0047074 has been renamed to \"hydroxyquinol 1,2-dioxygenase activity\" for the full EC:1.13.11.37 / RHEA:35595 reaction.\n## Summary\n\nAddressed issue #25870 by obsoleting GO:0018581 and using GO:0047074 as the replacement term for the full hydroxyquinol 1,2-dioxygenase reaction.\n\nChanges made:\n\n- Obsoleted GO:0018581 `hydroxyquinol 1,2-dioxygenase activity`, because it represents the RHEA:19441 sub-reaction rather than the full EC:1.13.11.37 activity.\n- Added `replaced_by: GO:0047074` to GO:0018581 and removed its active xrefs and asserted parent.\n- Renamed GO:0047074 from `4-hydroxycatechol 1,2-dioxygenase activity` to `hydroxyquinol 1,2-dioxygenase activity`.\n- Preserved the old GO:0047074 label as an exact synonym.\n- Kept EC:1.13.11.37 and RHEA:35595 as exact matches on GO:0047074, and qualified MetaCyc:RXN-10137 as a narrow match because it represents the non-enzymatic sub-reaction discussed in the issue.\n- Removed stale catalytic participant import axioms for GO:0018581 so the obsolete term no longer has imported superclass restrictions.\n\n## Validation\n\n- Pre-validation: `robot convert -i go-edit.obo -f obo` passed using the repo-local ROBOT wrapper.\n- External identifier checks:\n  - `runoak -i sqlite:obo:eccode info EC:1.13.11.37` confirmed hydroxyquinol 1,2-dioxygenase.\n  - `runoak -i sqlite:obo:rhea info RHEA:19441 RHEA:35595` confirmed RHEA:19441 is the sub-reaction and RHEA:35595 is the full maleylacetate-producing reaction.\n- Annotation impact: `runoak -i amigo: associations GO:0018581` returned no direct annotations.\n- Full validation: `make travis_build` passed in `obolibrary/odkfull:v1.6.1`.\n\n## Checklist\n\n- [x] PLAN: Issue context and comments reviewed; requester intent was clear.\n- [x] PRE-VALIDATION: Ontology parsed before edits.\n- [x] RESEARCH: N/A; no new literature references or PMIDs were introduced.\n- [x] TERM-SEARCH: GO:0018581 and GO:0047074 stanzas reviewed; usages of GO:0018581 checked.\n- [x] DESIGN-PATTERNS: Catalytic activity and obsolete-term patterns reviewed; no new logical definition added.\n- [x] EDITS: Used `obo-checkout.pl` / `obo-checkin.pl` for edits to GO term stanzas.\n- [x] RELATIONSHIPS: Removed active axioms from obsolete GO:0018581; retained the appropriate oxidoreductase parent on GO:0047074.\n- [x] SPECIALIZED-EDITS: Used term-obsoletion, reaction, mapping, and chemical-entity guidance.\n- [x] METADATA: Retained term tracker links; added obsolete comment and `replaced_by`.\n- [x] AUTOMATED-VALIDATION: `make travis_build` passed.\n- [x] REFERENCE-VALIDATION: RHEA and EC identifiers were checked; no PMID references introduced.\n- [x] CHANGES-COMMITTED: Ontology changes committed locally.\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
